Usage: unsourcemap [input] [--options] [value]
       unsourcemap [input] [--options=value]

Options:
  # SYSTEM
  -v, --version             Print current version.
  -h, --help                Print this help.

  # VALUE
  -i, --input               Directory for input.
  -o, --output              Directory for output.
  --mode                    Sourcemap mode, support `webpack` only.
  --replacement             Replacement for sanitize filepath.

  # BOOLEAN
  --force                   Overwrite output file.
  --async                   Use async writeFile.
  --verbose                 Log every file record.
  --dot                     Replace `/.` in webpack mode.

For more information, please visit the `README.md`.
